text: Taran Killam (born April 1, 1982) is an American actor, comedian and singer. He is a cast member on Saturday Night Live and one of the leading males on the show and plays a variety of characters and does a variety of impressions. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Actors from Culver City, California Category:Comedians from Los Angeles County, California Category:1982 births Category:Living people
